Tabitha used one of these
to kill that doll

542
00:30:35.920 --> 00:30:37.046
out by the settlement?

543
00:30:37.130 --> 00:30:38.173
Yeah.

544
00:30:38.256 --> 00:30:39.632
Well. tonight.
we're gonna see

545
00:30:39.716 --> 00:30:42.093
