562
00:31:25.345 --> 00:31:27.305
Oh. come on.
you know what I did.

563
00:31:27.388 --> 00:31:28.765
Yes.
Yes. I know what you did.

564
00:31:28.848 --> 00:31:30.475
Everyone knows what you did.
because...

565
00:31:30.558 --> 00:31:32.143
