- Manager at a retail store.

569
00:31:38.650 --> 00:31:40.485
Why... Why are those your
first two guesses?

570
00:31:40.568 --> 00:31:42.654
Well. I...

571
00:31:42.737 --> 00:31:45.573
That's a lot of wires.

572
00:31:45.657 --> 00:31:47.492
Yeah. we're kind of
in the middle of...

573
00:31:47.575 --> 00:31:49.410
