598
00:34:04.879 --> 00:34:06.506
Mind if I sit?

599
00:34:08.383 --> 00:34:09.550
Okay.

600
00:34:14.722 --> 00:34:17.767
Uh. I never got
the chance to say

601
00:34:17.850 --> 00:34:21.521
