healing pretty good.

606
00:34:39.914 --> 00:34:42.959
You gonna tell me
what happened?

607
00:34:43.042 --> 00:34:44.334
No.

608
00:34:50.174 --> 00:34:52.427
So. I guess you heard
about my mom.

609
00:34:53.886 --> 00:34:54.928
