611
00:34:58.808 --> 00:35:00.435
And that scares
the shit out of me.

612
00:35:00.518 --> 00:35:01.644
But why?

613
00:35:01.728 --> 00:35:03.479
'Cause every time someone
here feels

614
00:35:03.563 --> 00:35:04.981
