627
00:35:34.844 --> 00:35:37.597
So. part of your test is
getting mutilated?

628
00:35:43.561 --> 00:35:44.687
Sorry...

629
00:35:47.774 --> 00:35:48.900
I'm an asshole.

630
00:35:50.109 --> 00:35:53.071
There is a truth
behind all of this.

631
