687
00:39:54.312 --> 00:39:59.233
[bell ringing]

688
00:40:06.324 --> 00:40:08.784
- [indistinct chatter]
- Okay.

689
00:40:08.868 --> 00:40:10.077
Nice.

690
00:40:11.454 --> 00:40:13.289
Hey. Hey.
What are you doing?

691
00:40:13.372 --> 00:40:16.042
