like I'm doing?

692
00:40:16.125 --> 00:40:19.128
Let's get back in bed.

693
00:40:19.211 --> 00:40:20.713
Please.

694
00:40:22.381 --> 00:40:23.341
Okay.

695
00:40:25.509 --> 00:40:31.098
