to lay in bed for a minute?

715
00:41:13.140 --> 00:41:15.810
You never used
to be this sassy.

716
00:41:15.893 --> 00:41:19.230
Yeah. well. I gave birth
to a fucking monster. so.

717
00:41:19.313 --> 00:41:20.398
