What's goin' on?

742
00:42:30.259 --> 00:42:31.844
Um.

743
00:42:31.927 --> 00:42:33.512
I should be the one to go out
there tonight.

744
00:42:33.596 --> 00:42:36.182
- What? No.
- [Ellis clears throat]

745
00:42:36.265 --> 00:42:38.142
Hey. look.
it makes more sense.

746
00:42:38.225 --> 00:42:39.143
Why?

747
00:42:39.226 --> 00:42:40.561
