don't have to. That's why.

750
00:42:45.149 --> 00:42:48.527
No. I appreciate it.
but it's my plan. my risk.

751
00:42:48.611 --> 00:42:50.154
Dad. what if something
goes wrong?

752
00:42:50.237 --> 00:42:51.447
