to lose you here.

753
00:42:51.530 --> 00:42:53.157
Oh. oh. so we can afford
to lose Kenny?

754
00:42:53.240 --> 00:42:55.034
That's not what he's saying.
You know that.

755
00:42:55.117 --> 00:42:57.203
Listen. we're not having
this conversation.

756
00:42:57.286 --> 00:42:58.370
Dad...

757
00:42:58.454 --> 00:43:00.289
